Changing the DOS/4G Error Messages

    This example shows you how to change the wording of, or translate
    completely, the DOS/4G error messages.  For more information on
    changing the error messages see Chapter 8 of this manual.
    
    The example consists of the following files in the \EXAMPLE\ERRTEXT
    directory:
    
    USERERR.C   Sample program for remapping the DOS/4G error messages.
    
    ERRMSG.DOC  Format strings for the error messages.
    
    MAKEFILE    Polymake-configured makefile for creating USERERR.EXP
                using Microsoft C 6.0.
